    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a driver-focused E92 M3 featuring the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This unit retains its high-revving character with crisp throttle response via its eight individual throttle bodies. The 6-speed manual transmission offers precise engagement, paired with a functional M Variable Differential Lock for optimal power delivery. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive rod bearing service and throttle actuator replacement. While the aesthetics show minor road-wear consistent with its standing, the chassis remains taut with EDC dampers functioning as intended. A mechanically sound example for the purist seeking a linear power band and an 8,400 RPM redline.",
